      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THUNDERLASH (1) has been out of the placings at her last couple of runs but impressed when clocking a flying 21.59 over 390m at this track three starts back. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. HARA'S HAZEL (6) was always well back but did hit the line strongly late to finish 4th and beaten only 2.5 lengths (25.78) at this track. Has ability and is one of the better chances. MALAWI REBEL (3) was safely held last time out, finishing seventh at this track over 457m behind One Racket (26.50) in a Grade 6. Placed at his previous run. Cannot be underestimated. SKY KEEPING (7) cannot be left out after placing here at this trip last start.",
